{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act26side", "eventName": "空想花庭", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "HE-7", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "以愛相連", "storyInfo": "最後的聖餐已經開始，費德里科鳴銃打斷眾人爭執，拉特蘭諸人各自行動。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "39_g7_chapel", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loneliness_intro", "key": "$loneliness_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walk_stage"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walk_stage", "channel": "skz1", "loop": "false", "delay": 0.6}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walk_stage", "channel": "skt1", "loop": "false", "delay": 2.6}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walk_stage", "channel": "skt2", "loop": "false", "delay": 3.2}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_934_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_932_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_938_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_189", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_runstop", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_939_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_939_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "早安，主教閣下。", "name": "約里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_923_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "早安，又見面了，約里。請招呼一下其他人。", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#8$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_939_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好的。", "name": "約里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_934_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "主教閣下，我們......", "name": "膽怯的薩卡茲居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_934_1#1$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_923_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最近發生了很多事，蘇拉爾，我理解你的愁苦。", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#8$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_934_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們是不是不該來？拉特蘭來的那些人會不會......", "name": "膽怯的薩卡茲居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_934_1#1$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_923_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒關係。", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#8$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "生活在安布羅修修道院的人，都有資格進入禮拜堂，十年來都是如此。", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#8$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就坐在第一排吧，蘇拉爾，像以前一樣，不用緊張。", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#8$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉特蘭人不會打擾已經開始的聖餐儀式。", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#8$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_outside", "volume": 0.1, "loop": "true", "channel": "crwd"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "各位，請入座。", "name": "修道院主教"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "接下來是餐前禱告的時間。請各位等待，請各位聆聽，請各位感受此刻的寧靜。", "name": "修道院主教"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "crwd", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "39_i09", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.7, "yScale": 1.7, "x": 450.0, "y": 100.0, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.7, "yScaleFrom": 1.7, "xScaleTo": 1.7, "yScaleTo": 1.7, "xTo": 380.0, "yTo": 60.0, "duration": 15.0}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$monastery_sad_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "本人斯特凡諾·托雷格羅薩，安布羅修修道院主教，向各位居民致意。", "name": "修道院主教"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我習慣用“居民”來稱呼大家，而非“信徒”“同胞”或者其他。", "name": "修道院主教"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "世人，包括我們自己，對薩科塔和薩卡茲的印象從來如此，律法與野蠻、秩序與暴力、和平與戰爭、天使與惡魔云云......", "name": "修道院主教"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "光環與角是我們醒目的體貌，是鐫刻進生命的符號，我們各自都是行走在這片大地上會引來關注的群體。", "name": "修道院主教"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但過去的數千個日子裡，我們共同生活，今天又聚集於此，分領聖餐，共享蔭護與賜福。", "name": "修道院主教"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大家來到修道院的時間有長有短，但最短的也已逾十年。", "name": "修道院主教"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在更長的時間裡，我們無從確定自己是否已遭離棄，或已被遺忘。我們未知前路，而又身處險地，終於在無人知曉的歧路相逢。", "name": "修道院主教"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "39_i09", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 2.0, "xScale": 1.7, "yScale": 1.7, "y": 100.0}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"image": "39_i09", "fadetime": 0.5, "xScaleFrom": 1.7, "yScaleFrom": 1.7, "xScaleTo": 1.7, "yScaleTo": 1.7, "yTo": 60.0, "duration": 15.0}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們並非沒有矛盾，我們並非沒有隱秘，但我們試著彼此接納。", "name": "修道院主教"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "此刻，禮拜堂中的所有人，我們知曉對方的名姓，瞭解彼此的習慣，我們自覺分享食物，願意為對方抵禦風雨。", "name": "修道院主教"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們共同驅趕野獸，對抗匪徒；我們共同燒製磚石，整理路面；我們修補每一扇窗戶，耕種每一壟糧食。", "name": "修道院主教"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們親如手足，我們彼此愛護，我們將對方的安寧視作自己的所求。", "name": "修道院主教"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們的聯繫如此緊密，共同的體貌或天然的感應不足以證明什麼，信仰的差異或理念的分歧不足以阻隔什麼。", "name": "修道院主教"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我們苦熬長夜，卻禁受不住晨光熹微之時的寒冷。", "name": "修道院主教"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "39_i09", "fadetime": 2.0, "xScale": 1.0, "yScale": 1.0}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"image": "39_i09", "fadetime": 0.5, "xScaleFrom": 1.0, "yScaleFrom": 1.0, "xScaleTo": 0.85, "yScaleTo": 0.85, "duration": 12.0}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "遠道而來的拉特蘭特使、執行者，以及......異域的使者，他們各有盤算，帶來了新的希望，也帶來了令人苦痛的抉擇。", "name": "修道院主教"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們本就殘破的樑柱在大火中傾塌，我們可敬可靠的手足在矛盾中殞命......", "name": "修道院主教"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯特凡諾·托雷格羅薩想要謀求盡善的結果，哪怕那是一個未經驗證的答案，為此我祈求各位的原諒。", "name": "修道院主教"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "安布羅修修道院並非樂土，但它是我們共同的“家園”。", "name": "修道院主教"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我相信我們會做出一樣的選擇。", "name": "修道院主教"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "禱告結束，請各位領取並享用聖餐。", "name": "修道院主教"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "39_g8_outsidepath", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_925_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "疼嗎？", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_925_1#6$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還好。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4015_spuria_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別嘴硬了，奧倫，我都聽見你上下牙打顫的聲音了。", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#1$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "力氣再怎麼大，狙擊銃銃管的威力也不會大過它的子彈。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_925_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不介意真給你一顆。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_925_1#6$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我能清晰感受到你的憤怒......真是強烈。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在為我冒犯了你信仰的純粹而憤怒。這樣的憤怒，說明你正是作為一個拉特蘭人在思考問題。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的任務是將安布羅修修道院帶回拉特蘭，救助其中意外離散的薩科塔同胞。而我的目標，則是維護拉特蘭之所以為拉特蘭的合理性。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放下那些感性的念頭吧，蕾繆安，我們從來都沒有矛盾。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_925_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你依然在詭辯。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_925_1#6$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這套靠用冠冕堂皇的大道理唬人的說辭，是從維多利亞那些公爵，還是從哥倫比亞那些商人身上學來的，萬國信使奧倫？", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_925_1#6$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我說過，突然出現的野獸會驚嚇到流浪的人，我不會坐視一場屠殺發生。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_925_1#6$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特勤部隊馬上就會就位，你阻攔不了我。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#7$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_925_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我大可以制服你，然後再想辦法搞定他們。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_925_1#6$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "除非你真正對著我的腦袋給我一顆子彈，不然這樣的偷襲不會成功第二次了，蕾繆安。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#7$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_925_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_gunload", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是嗎？", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_925_1#7$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4015_spuria_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等，學姐，奧倫，不是吧，你們要來真的——", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#3$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$pistol", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "39_i07", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xFrom": 0.0, "yFrom": 0.0, "xTo": 510.0, "yTo": 120.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.8, "yScaleFrom": 1.8, "xScaleTo": 1.8, "yScaleTo": 1.8, "duration": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "突兀的一聲轟鳴截斷了在場三人的話頭。"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$pistol", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$pistol", "volume": 0.9, "loop": "false", "channel": "shot", "delay": 0.4}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "ystrength": 60.0, "vibrato": 40.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.2, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "39_i07", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來不及反應，緊接著又是同樣的兩聲，近得讓人覺得守護銃彷彿是貼在耳邊發射，有那麼幾秒，他們甚至聽不見自己的心跳聲。"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "火舌在清晨濕潤的空氣中舔出傷口一般的長痕，天光乍破。"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_gunload", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$exciting_intro", "key": "$exciting_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 4.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉特蘭公證所執行者費德里科，鳴銃示警。", "name": "費德里科"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "教皇廳樞機輔佐官蕾繆安、萬國信使奧倫，還有隨我同來的第六廳技術員斯普莉雅，立即停止你們無謂的爭鬥。", "name": "費德里科"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒有必要理解你們的立場，更沒有必要調停你們的衝突。", "name": "費德里科"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "任務尚未完成，新生的變故尚有繼續惡化的可能，這座異鄉的修道院此刻需要秩序。", "name": "費德里科"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果如你們所說，你們沒有矛盾，卻爭執難斷，擁有共感的群體卻依舊有崩解的可能......", "name": "費德里科"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼我來維持秩序。", "name": "費德里科"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鳴銃同樣是對外面特勤部隊的示警，拉特蘭的官方軍隊決不能貿然進入安布羅修修道院。", "name": "費德里科"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奧倫，你私下調動了他們，那麼就由你來負責約束。讓他們後退一公里待命。", "name": "費德里科"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蕾繆安，斯普莉雅，你們此前與居住在這裡的薩科塔和薩卡茲接觸較多，接下來負責安撫他們的情緒，防止事態惡化。", "name": "費德里科"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "完成任務後，前往禮拜堂會合。里凱萊已經發現了一些線索，正在追查。", "name": "費德里科"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而我會儘快找出這幾起異常事件背後的人。", "name": "費德里科"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "奧倫"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "斯普莉雅"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "蕾繆安"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在，行動。", "name": "費德里科"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "39_g10_monasterycorridor_d", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "禱告結束，請各位領取並享用聖餐。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#6$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉......緊趕慢趕，終究還是沒來得及。", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#6$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#6$1", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.3}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "禮拜堂的門留了一條縫，里凱萊貼過去看了看，領完無酵餅和葡萄酒的眾人已經回到了座位上。"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "隔得遠遠的，禱告台上年邁的主教抬頭看向門外，里凱萊有種和對方對視了的錯覺。"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorclosequite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_gunequip", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_handcuff", "volume": 0.7, "delay": 0.2}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "里凱萊停頓了一秒，然後將禮拜堂的大門合緊。他想了想，又從腰間掏出一支備用銃柄將門的把手別住。"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "差不多了，接下來就只能等裡面......結束了。", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#1$1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#1$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$pistol", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔？這麼果斷，看來是費德里科......他都遇到了情況，那這邊就只剩下我一個人收尾了......", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#5$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真麻煩啊。", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#8$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "早知道，還不如領另外那份去薩爾貢調查失蹤的萬國信使的任務呢，遠是遠了點，但那幫和黃沙打交道的傢伙情感總不會這麼複雜。", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#8$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難不成，我註定要成為一個工作狂？還真是應了那句不知道哪裡聽來的俗語，“命不由人”。", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#8$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$bullet_loading"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔，膛線與觸發裝置正常，守護銃隨時可以使用。", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#1$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萬一裡面的人待會兒都......一發一個能解決嗎......子彈可能不夠。難不成用拳頭？", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#1$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等回到拉特蘭，得向公證所申請一次獎勵休假才行，這個工作量，不可能不給批吧。", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#1$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}